{"type":"text","timestamp":1775843425043,"sessionID":"ses_2877ecc48ffeLfo6bU8734TLmk","part":{"id":"prt_d78842be2001zNCTy0TDNwZzen","messageID":"msg_d78840bf70016PLHKSBSUygefL","sessionID":"ses_2877ecc48ffeLfo6bU8734TLmk","type":"text","text":"Delta spec for AR-005 has been written successfully at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md`.\n\nThe spec covers:\n- Sandbox Controller architecture for `pkg/workloadmanager`\n- AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter sandbox creation flows\n- Session management (create, get, delete)\n- Kubernetes integration via client-go\n- HTTP handlers with request validation\n- Error handling and response formats\n- Labels/annotations management\n- Health check endpoint\n\nEach requirement includes multiple GIVEN/WHEN/THEN acceptance scenarios following OpenSpec format.","time":{"start":1775843425042,"end":1775843425042}}}
